---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Freedom Mobility NY"
  description="How Freedom Mobility NY collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>Freedom Mobility NY is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or contact us for home accessibility services.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Contact information you provide through our form (name, phone, email, message).</li>
      <li>Basic usage data (pages visited) via standard web analytics if enabled in the future.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your consultation requests and provide our services.</li>
      <li>To communicate with you about appointments, quotes, or follow-ups.</li>
      <li>To improve our website and services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted service providers (e.g. installation partners) only as needed to fulfill your request. We comply with applicable New York privacy laws.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions: <a href="mailto:info@freedommobilityny.com">info@freedommobilityny.com</a> or call (585) 488-0771.</p>

    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block mt-8 bg-slate-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl no-underline">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
